      </div>

      <div class="w-full p-8">
        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            I specialise in designing and implementing robust storage solutions using enterprise-grade open source technologies. Whether you need a new NAS deployment, storage expansion, or performance optimisation of existing systems, I can help create reliable storage infrastructure that meets your data management needs while ensuring data integrity and accessibility.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2">
            <Database className="text-themepink w-6" />
            <h5 class="text-base dark:text-gray-200 text-gray-800 font-bold m-0">
              TrueNAS &amp; ZFS
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            As a TrueNAS specialist, I work extensively with both SCALE and CORE editions to deliver enterprise-grade storage solutions. ZFS provides unmatched data integrity, snapshot capabilities, and efficient replication. I can help you leverage advanced features like dataset management, compression, and deduplication to optimise your storage infrastructure while ensuring maximum data protection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2">
            <Network className="text-themepink w-6" />
            <h5 class="text-base dark:text-gray-200 text-gray-800 font-bold m-0">
              Network Storage Protocols
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            Modern storage solutions need to support various access protocols. I implement and configure NFS, SMB/CIFS, and iSCSI to ensure your storage is accessible across different platforms and operating systems. This includes setting up proper permissions, optimising performance, and ensuring secure access to shared resources.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2">
            <HardDriveDownload className="text-themepink w-6" />
            <h5 class="text-base dark:text-gray-200 text-gray-800 font-bold m-0">
              Backup &amp; Disaster Recovery
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            Data protection is critical in today's digital environment. I design comprehensive backup strategies utilising ZFS snapshots, replication, and both on-site and off-site backup solutions. This includes implementing automated backup schedules, testing recovery procedures, and ensuring your data is protected against hardware failure, user errors and other potential disasters.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2">
            <Box className="text-themepink w-6" />
            <h5 class="text-base dark:text-gray-200 text-gray-800 font-bold m-0">
              Object Storage &amp; S3
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            Modern applications often require object storage capabilities. I implement solutions like MinIO and TrueNAS's built-in S3-compatible storage to provide scalable, reliable object storage. This enables cloud-native applications while maintaining data sovereignty and reducing costs compared to cloud storage providers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2">
            <KeyRound className="text-themepink w-6" />
            <h5 class="text-base dark:text-gray-200 text-gray-800 font-bold m-0">
              Data Protection &amp; Security
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            Security is paramount when it comes to data storage. I implement robust access controls, encryption at rest and in transit, and audit logging to ensure your data remains secure. This includes configuring RAID arrays for redundancy, implementing ZFS encryption, and setting up secure remote access to storage resources.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-1 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 mb-1 mt-2">
            <Code className="text-themepink w-6" />
            <h5 class="text-base dark:text-gray-200 text-gray-800 font-bold m-0">
              How I Can Help
            </h5>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            By understanding your storage requirements, data protection needs, and performance expectations, I can help design and implement a storage solution that provides the right balance of performance, reliability, and cost-effectiveness. Whether you're looking to deploy a new NAS system, optimise existing storage, or implement a comprehensive backup strategy, I can help you navigate the technical complexities and deliver a solution that meets your needs.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-3">
            Many of my clients start with basic NAS requirements but quickly realise the benefits of enterprise features like snapshots, replication, and automated backups. I can help you build a scalable storage infrastructure that grows with your needs while maintaining data integrity and accessibility.
          </p>
        </div>

